## üõ†Ô∏è Development

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/pingera/pingera-cli.git
cd pingera-cli

# Install in development mode
pip install -e .

# Test the CLI (after installation)
pngr --help

# Run tests
python -m pytest tests/
```

